(2535, 107, 'maplist_description', 'Upscale your evening with drinks in the cocktail lounge of a stunning Georgian Town house in the heart of Creative Territory. An award winning cocktail menu with a stunning antique ambiance.'),
(2538, 107, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">When hanging out in central creative territory (Clerkenwell) there seems to be an unlimited array of "quirky" drinking spots but very few that feel \'upmarket\'. Where can you go if you feel like upscaling your evening, ordering G&amp;T while sitting in a posh cocktail lounge of say, a Georgian townhouse? Well, you would be in luck!</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Zetter Townhouse boasts as award winning cocktail bar with a sumptuous antique vibe that makes you feel unusually at homely and cozy.  There are also 13 gorgeous Georgian bedrooms to entice the out-of-towners, though you might feel more like you are staying in the home of an eccentric great aunt, rather than a hotel!</p>\r\n&nbsp;'),
