(2599, 245, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">If you are not lucky enough to live in London and require somewhere to rest your weary head, there are few better spots to do so, than the Hoxton Hotel.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">The fact this venue is known more for its bar and restaurant is unjust, as the cool, Scandinavian inspired rooms are simple (compact) yet luxurious (rainfall shower heads) and definitely stylish, offering all you could want in an over night stay in London town.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">An ideal spot to ogle the creative folk from the city, who will often be found sipping martinis in the large lobby bar or tucking into a well deserved mac n cheese in the Hoxton Grill restaurant. One of the hotels most admired spots is the outdoor courtyard area which is lush, green and covered so it can be used all year round for dinner or entertaining.</p>'),
