(2619, 94, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Understandably if someone asks if you fancy a trip to the Hospital - you would probably politely decline, but that was until this hub of creativity popped up. A ginormous venue, covering 7 floors is like a mini city, with hotel rooms, a TV studio, with multiple screening rooms and performance spaces as well as the obligatory bar and restaurant.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Admittedly a swanky establishment (they have REN soaps and creams in the loos) such as this comes at a cost, you won\'t find any riff-raff in here. Expect to see a bubbling bunch of media darr-lings enoying the treats at the martini bar and a scattering of suits,however to impress a big client or mingle with the creative bigwigs - this is your ticket.</p>'),
