(2718, 90, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p2">They say, good things come in small packages - and that is the perfect motto for Ducksoup.</p>\r\n<p class="p2">It has a real "local" feel to it, with cosy cafe décor and ambiance, so much so, that you can even select your own choice of vinyl to play while you eat. The menu changes almost daily, using the best season’s produce. Imagine the best bits of Mediterranean tapas style dining, mixed with some classic British bite and middle Eastern twist – a recipe for success.</p>\r\n<p class="p2">In the centre of Soho – it is one of the few restaurants that doesn\'t take itself too seriously just offers a great atmosphere perfect to unwind with friends or colleagues.</p>'),
