(2740, 89, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Some bars and restaurants in London are just not enough to entertain the overactive mind of a creative which is why Drink Shop Do is a dream come true. This cafe by day, bar by night - enables you to drink and eat whilst embarking on some very fun tasks, from the more normal “Let’s get quizzical” quiz night, to "Pimp my shades" workshops!</p>\r\n<p class="p1">The eclectic all-day menu serves up delights from ham hock, quinoa salads and cheese and biscuits so it’s ideal for a light lunch or join them after your work day is done for bubbles, beers and cocktails for their amazing evening workshops.</p>'),
