(2778, 31, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Breakfast really is the most important meal of the day at the UKs first speciality Cereal Café has opened in Shoreditch, with 120 different types of cereal from around the world. Relive your childhood eating cereal for breakfast, lunch or dinner in nostalgic 80\'s/90\'s surroundings.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Ideal for a breakfast meeting<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>with your colleagues or impress your quirkiest clients. What better way to discuss that business proposal, than over a bowel of “lucky charms”.</p>'),
