(2797, 85, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Grow \'curiouser and curiouser\' as you escape to wonderland with a trip to Calooh Calley. An indulgent cocktail bar nestled in Shoreditch where you are transported to the middle of a Lewis Carroll novel.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Fitted with its very own secret wardrobe(a definite highlight and a ingenious photo opportunity) that you enter to discover other private rooms, plus bundles of eccentric décor to take in, you really can feel like a character in a story book.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span></p>\r\n<p class="p1">If you are not a lover of literature or you think it all sounds far too "quirky\'" for you, you\'ll be pleased to know not just \'mad hatters\' visit, it is generally a pretty awesome cosy cocktails bar with a really great cocktail list and talented bartenders so even just for that reason, it\'s worth a visit!</p>'),
