(2832, 77, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Set up by two friends who had passion for decadent drinks and deserts, the Basement State is a Parisian styled bar with an intimate feel.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">One of the few destination in London where grown-ups can go for ice-cream, sample their<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>to-die-for<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>deserts, whether it be the Peanut Butter Jelly Times, or a white chocolate Hemispherical Dream.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">The sugar overload is even more satisfying when accompanied by a cocktail in this divine setting.</p>'),
