(2851, 76, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Positioned on one of the most famous streets in London, this dress down barnyard is a refreshing dining experience. Packed with the capitals cool kids, Barnyard specialises in simple hearty grub.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">A friendly vibe, that is both affordable and fun – so whether you’re taking the kids along – or you want to relive your favourite childhood meals, you can tuck into sausage rolls, fry-ups and<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>bubble ’n’ squeak.;</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Those wanting a low calorie, organic goodness should avoid – this is gourmet junk food at its very best.</p>'),
