(2950, 91, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Snuck away down an alley, that ordinarily you might choose to avoid - is the award-winning Hakkasan, and you\'ll be so glad you made the trip.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Its quite a memorable place and from the minute you are greeted by the stylish front desk staff and get a whiff of the delicious incense - you feel that mini fist pump feeling of \'yes I have arrived\'. There\'s much to take in, from the impressive bar, demur lighting (which is on the verge of being too dark) and Chinoiserie decadence.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">A perfect setting for a special occasion, whether it be celebrating the brief you have won or the promotion you have received - but keep for real treat as dining in a Michelin starred venue - does not come cheap.</p>'),
