(2971, 87, 'locations__the_content', 'With a cool twist on the old fashioned chicken spots in the UK, \'Chicken Shop\' is the hot property in London. The Balham haunt is actually more than just chicken – aptly named ‘Chicken and Egg shop’. Serving the classic staple chicken menu plus incredible side dishes (the same as it’s sister restaurants in Kentish Town, Whitechapel<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>and Holborn) however this venue serves up breakfast too! So whether you want to tuck into eggs for breakfast or their famous marinated free-range birds<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>for dinner – the chicken and egg shop is simply spectacular.'),
