(2988, 81, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">One of the only 24 hour licensed bars in London where you can still feel sophisticated.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">An ideal place to head when you just don\'t want the night to end or you’ve been burning the late night oil at work and need a big of fun before heading straight home.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Spread across three floors each with gorgeous Moroccan interior, Beduin is unlike another night spot. With skilled bartenders dedicated to the art of mixology a delicious Middle Eastern menu and shisha pipes – it has all you need for a brilliant night.</p>'),
