(3106, 104, 'locations__the_content', 'An award-winning<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>bar and lounge that sits comfortably below one of the famous ROKA restaurants in Charlotte Street, Soho. This stylish restaurant bar, is so much more than a warm up act for it\'s upstairs diners, at Shōchū you can sample the Japanese robatayaki cuisine and sip wonderful cocktails in the striking yet comfortable surroundings.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Its spot is ideal for creatives needing a quick escape from a mad day, where you can unwind in this central yet secluded space.'),
