(3137, 106, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Feel like you need to escape? Transport yourself to a quaint corner table, in a stunning café in central Europe. But if you can\'t quite make it there, the next best thing is to book a table at the famous Wolseley.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">It really is an incredible venue with its high ceilings, stunning chandeliers you really get a WOW sensation as you enter and take in the grand décor of this Grade II listed building.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">If you are a trendy media type, this will be your go-to venue for a working breakfast or post-work debrief over a chilled Sauvignon Blanc. The menu is sits somewhere between British, French and Austrian cuisines, the dishes are all very rich in flavour, and the drinks list is extensive (and very fancy). The price tags are high-end, as you would expect from such a grand venue in Mayfair, but you in return you do get the full VIP treatment from their staff.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">(Also it\'s worth remembering that their Afternoon Tea is delicious and competitively priced, so next time your Mum is down to visit, this is a winner.)</p>'),
(3138, 106, '_locations__the_content', 'field_56221eea97ca0'),
(3139, 106, 'maplist_description', 'Be transported to a grand cafe in a European city as you enter the grand and stunning Wolseley.  Get the full VIP treatment in this top notch restaurant in Mayfair and mingle with celebrities to trendy media types.'),
