(3600, 297, 'locations__the_content', 'The Boundary is a classy venue for those in the know. Expect to rub shoulders with a host of Designers, Fashionistas and Architects, who travel to this spot from the far corners of London. Situated inside a <span style="line-height: 1.5;">super stylish Victorian warehouse, it is nice to see The Boundary has preserved many of its industrial features. </span>\r\n\r\nFar more than just a bar, The Boundary hosts 2 restaurants (an A La Carte and a grill), 2 bars  (a basement cocktail bar and roof terrace area). An area on the roof is definitely the \'golden ticket\' of the city, with hoards of people often queuing for a space so arrive early to avoid disappointment. However if you are dining out with your best clients the underground French restaurant is much more sophisticated and quaint.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
