(3776, 105, 'locations__the_content', 'What do we all love about the Scandinavian way of life? It\'s cool, stylish and modern - and this is what\'s served up in Sticks n Sushi, Denmark’s latest export. The quality of the food is top class, when you dine on their ‘Salmon Carpaccio’ and ‘Sashimi Sea Bass’ you could be fooled into believing you were dining at Nobu, but thankfully when the reasonably priced bill arrives you are supremely happy and would want to be anywhere else.\r\n\r\nThey claim to employ their staff based on personality, but that’s actually believable when you see just how sweet and personable they all are.\r\n\r\nTop pick for sushi lovers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
