(3809, 103, 'locations__the_content', '[embed]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=56QHHzImzO0[/embed]\r\n<p class="p1">Appealing to the Londoner who likes their home comforts, but wants something a bit different.  The people who flock to the Old Red Cow do so because its the ideal combination of local pub and speciality crafte beer house, filling the belly\'s of creatives with quirky, unique and special tasting ales and beers.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">You may THINK you know all there is to know about beer, but the bartenders are really knowledgeable about the varieties and techniques, so be prepared to be "schooled" on beer. And whatever you do, don\'t go in and ask for a bottle of bud - it will just insult them.</p>\r\n<p class="p1"></p>'),
