(3875, 101, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">The Portside Parlour is an authentic underground Rum bar hidden away in East London, as long as you are not put off by entering through a toilet. The quirky cubicle door way, asks you to “flush to enter” and once you do you will be welcomed into a candle-lit cocktail bar with a nautical vibe.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Sink into the soft leather sofas and sip their ridiculously good list cocktails, and over 50 different types of rum to ensure all your stresses sail away.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">This hangout was only meant to be a short-term popup but due to popular demand has had its residency extended so make sure you go and share the love so this gem stays for longer.</p>'),
