(3908, 100, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Ariba Ariba. Get your mexican ON. If tequila is your poison, then this is your new haven. Hidden below Soho\'s best Mexican restaurant is this "loco" little cocktail bar. It\'s a members only policy (however you can join easily enough and feel like a VIP) but unlike many private members clubs - you don\'t need to earn a certain amount or work ibn a particular industry - you just have to be FUN (for example the like the sort of people who will dance on the tables.) Once your membership is sorted, the only other issue is getting into the venue via a ladder-like staircase but once you are in - you\'re in for a lot of fun.</p>'),
