(3941, 99, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Cycling and coffee - sounds like an accident waiting to happen! However, it would appear there are some crazy folk of London who thought the two would be a match made in heaven - and turns out they were right! Look Mum no hands has taken the South Bank by storm. A relaxed café space (that part resembles an art studio) with a fully functioning workshop filled with clever mechanics to solve all your bike riding problems.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Even if bicycles are not your thing, it\'s a buzzing pit stop to meet pals and there are also other events available from speed dating to knitting classes (see what we mean, there really is something for everyone!)</p>'),
