(3974, 98, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Nightjar is like a time machine dedicated to the speak-easy culture through the ages. Hidden behind a dark, unlit door way, Night jar is an underground cocktail bar close to Old Street Station.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">They have marvellous live music every night (mostly jazz or blues) and the place gives a real intimate feel with low level lighting and cosy tables.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Their cocktail menu is playful and divided into historical eras (pre-Prohibition, post-war etc) and each is presented in a weird and wonderful way. Their jugs of cocktails are also a brilliant way to get you and your creative pals in the mood.</p>'),
