(4040, 96, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Whether Jazz, Gypsy Stomp or Rock \'n\' Roll takes your fancy - Jamboree play it all. Get your hippie-on and allow yourself to be transported to 70\'s Parisian style den, as you peel back the heavy velvet drapes and enter the low-lit club. While the mix of people is \'eclectic\' to say the least - it\'s one of the few places you can go and feel instantly accepted because honestly, anything goes.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Flat shoes are advisable as you will be up on your feet swaying to the music in no time at all – especially if you sample the absinthe which is available. The perfect place the creative, that craves something different.</p>'),
