(6455, 397, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p1">Fitzrovia is where money meets cool and Fitzrovia’s Salt Yard is where media professionals meet the best tapas of their lives. There’s great wine here and a decidedly trendy bar, but the sensational food is the focus of everything.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Serving both Italian and Spanish dishes, Salt Yard’s menu is a who’s who of the best cuts of everything: Isle of Mull salmon with saffron, Iberico Pressa, porcini arancini are words which make the mouth water instantly. This is a great place to treat someone special after you meet for shopping on Oxford Street, but be prepared to dole out around £8 per dish.</p>'),
