(9903, 479, 'locations__the_content', '<p class="p2">Contrary to popular belief, Dalston Superstore (murder anyone who calls it Dalston Superstores) is not misleadingly named. A superstore is meant to sell everything you need, right? Well, if you think about it, Dalston Superstore <i>does </i>sell everything the average Dalstoner needs. Here you can find all-day brunch for all Dalston’s hung-over freelancers, a constant roster of queer-centric exhibitions and events, and legendary gay club nights ClamJam and Homodrop. Cutting-edge art, avocado-heavy food and famous dance floor. See? Everything the average Dalstoner needs.</p>'),
