(11535, 31, 'wp_review_desc', 'They could have had a more tasteful pun. Cereal Offender would have been a bit less obvious. Super Bowl would have been good too! But they went with Cereal Killer. \r\n\r\nWhat are you actually saying when you bring a friend, client or mother in here? The basic message is that you’re ‘cool’ and you really love cereal (and that you want to drop the hashtag #cerealkillers. With the biggest array of cereals you could ever ask for, you can revert back to your childhood and enjoy a bowl of lucky charms. But at £3.70 for a bowl, you have to really love cereal to embrace this experience.  \r\n'),
(11536, 105, 'maplist_description', 'Top class sushi in stylish Scandinavian surroundings, proves a welcome haven from the hustle and bustle of Covent Garden.'),
