(11544, 104, 'wp_review_desc', 'Forget about sake, Shōchū is infact the national spirit of Japan and aptly it is also the name of a sultry cocktail bar snuggled below one of the famous ROKA robatayaki restaurants in Soho.  \r\n\r\nSo much more than a warm up act for its upstairs diners, with wacky murals and a far out drinks menu it\'s got a real authentic feel, and thus you really should get involved in one of the Shōchū infused drinks - it would be rude not too.\r\n\r\n'),
(11545, 103, 'maplist_description', 'For Londoner who loves their local but wants to sample something a bit different. You\'ll find the largest variety of speciality craft beer house, in comfy surroundings.'),
(11546, 102, 'wp_review_desc', 'As far as drinks spots go, a vaulted basement gives quite an exclusive feel, wouldn\'t you agree? Unlike the many (many, many) secret speak-easy bars that are popping up in London, Purl provides guests with a real vintage vibe.\r\n\r\nPicture baroque artistic influences, rich flock wallpaper and a lot of velvet - and you\'ll get the gist. Their drinks list is divine, and you can expect everything from fogs and airs and foams protruding from your glass, treating all your senses to a something pretty special. \r\n\r\nImpress your pals with this find - the password to enter is "hair of the dog"'),
(11547, 102, 'maplist_description', 'A vaulted basement cocktail bar with baroque interior gives an exclusive experience to satisfy all the senses.  '),
(11548, 101, 'wp_review_desc', 'Eye eye captain, what\'s this? Another speak-easy bar in Shoreditch? Well yes, but this one has a very fun twist. Filled with all things nautical, (think Pirates and bundles of rum) you\'ll find a treasure trove so long as you are not put off by the fact you have to enter through a dormant toilet!\r\n\r\nDespite a heavy rum inspired drinks menu, there are a host of other strong options in the form of old fashioned whiskies and gins and spirits.\r\n\r\nThe Portside Parlour is the brain child of two Aussie fella\'s, so you can expect a laid back vibe and lot of drink mixing.  \r\n'),
