(71, 1, '2015-10-09 16:59:10', '2015-10-09 16:59:10', '<p class="p1">This restored Victorian public convenience (dormant for years) has now been lovingly transformed into a quirky cafe serving breakfast and light lunch.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>If you can overlook the fact you are sipping a coffee in an old toilet you will enjoy a delicious brunch and embrace to quirky decor.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>One of the few places in central London you can kick back with a coffee without bumping into a colleague or client while you are trying to scoff vanilla dipped French toast, in peace.</p>', 'The Attendant', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-attendant', '', '', '2015-12-15 14:28:39', '2015-12-15 14:28:39', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/mct-wordpress/?post_type=maplist&#038;p=71', 0, 'maplist', '', 0),
