(79, 1, '2015-10-09 17:45:15', '2015-10-09 17:45:15', '<p class="p1">BBB (as it is commonly known) is the younger sister venue to the first successful BBB establishment in Notting Hill, but despite the big boots it needs to fill, BBB Shoreditch hits the spot.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Its grand entrance is striking in its rather quirky neighbourhood. Enter into an opulent cocktail bar and restaurant with sultry decor and atmosphere.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Order from their top notch menu or just have drinks in the bar area, and if you want the night to continue, head down to their basement club later where DJS play into the small hours.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">As well as dinner, lunch menus are available and the venue has proved to be a very popular spot for client lunches for local agencies to close that deal.</p>', 'Beach Blanket Babylon', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'beach-blanket-babylon', '', '', '2015-12-18 13:00:34', '2015-12-18 13:00:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/mct-wordpress/?post_type=maplist&#038;p=79', 0, 'maplist', '', 0),
