(81, 1, '2015-10-09 17:55:00', '2015-10-09 17:55:00', '<p class="p1">One of the only 24 hour licensed bars in London where you can still feel sophisticated.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">An ideal place to head when you just don\'t want the night to end or you’ve been burning the late night oil at work and need a big of fun before heading straight home.</p>\r\n<p class="p1">Spread across three floors each with gorgeous Moroccan interior, Beduin is unlike another night spot. With skilled bartenders dedicated to the art of mixology a delicious Middle Eastern menu and shisha pipes – it has all you need for a brilliant night.</p>', 'Beduin Bar', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'beduin-bar', '', '', '2015-10-19 19:06:29', '2015-10-19 19:06:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/mct-wordpress/?post_type=maplist&#038;p=81', 0, 'maplist', '', 0),
