(216, 1, '2015-10-16 11:16:10', '2015-10-16 11:16:10', 'Coffee, it’s so much more than just a hot drink. It is a source of joy, the medicine that makes everything better, the refreshment that turns us from moody morning people to idea inspiring ideas people.\r\n\r\nBut not all coffee is the same, and while a Costa, a Starbucks or even a Pret-a-Manger can treat your coffee fix, there are some establishments that soothe more than your caffeine craving:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Ask for Janice, 50-52 Long Lane, Farringdon, EC1A 9EJ</strong>\r\n\r\nEast London has some excellent cafes, but one of the most popular has to be Ask for Janice. Serving coffee and a delicious range of breakfast treats s from 7:30am, this is certainly one for the early birds - although even if you sleep in, you can stop by for a delicious lunch and dinner taking in the wonderful social atmosphere.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Coffee works project, 96-98 Islington High Street, Islington, London N1 8EG</strong>\r\n\r\nIslington is one of the buzziest spots in London and throughout the day the Coffee Works Project is filled with coffee lovers. It is part of the new wave of independent speciality coffee houses that offer a wide array of coffees and teas from around the world in a wonderfully relaxed environment.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>The Attendant, 27A Foley Street, London, W1W 6DY</strong>\r\n\r\nThis restored Victorian public convenience (dormant for years) has now been lovingly transformed into a quirky cafe serving breakfast and light lunch. If you can overlook the fact you are sipping a coffee in an old toilet you will enjoy a delicious brunch and embrace to quirky decor.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Climpsons &amp; Sons 67 Broadway Market, London E8</strong>\r\n\r\nExpect one of the warmest welcomes you will find in London at this family run coffee house. Be prepared to queue as this café is extremely popular with the locals. This is a business of real coffee enthusiasts who roast their own espresso beans serving incredible coffee and delicious food.\r\n\r\nSo whether it’s a morning brew or a late afternoon lift you’re craving - the creatives of London, need look no further than these cool coffee spots.', 'More than just a coffee...', 'Source of joy, the medicine that makes everything better, the refreshment that turns us from moody morning people', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '115-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-16 11:16:10', '2015-10-16 11:16:10', '', 115, 'http://localhost:8888/mct-wordpress/115-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
