(262, 1, '2015-10-17 12:25:32', '2015-10-17 12:25:32', '<p class="p1">The little sister of Blues Kitchen Camden, this is one of the coolest venues in East London!<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>A huge impressive building play host to this New Orleans inspired music hall. Feast on huge portions of Cajun comfort food<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>menu and sample of their classic bourbon inspired cocktails in a cosy booth. Live music kicks off around 9 pm with an eclectic mix from blues to swing and DJs play most night until 3am! There is even sometimes a bucking bronco that pops up for those feeling brave – but whether your in the saddle or not – this place is a party every night of the week.</p>', 'The Blues Kitchen', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '83-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-10-17 12:25:32', '2015-10-17 12:25:32', '', 83, 'http://localhost:8888/mct-wordpress/83-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
