(601, 2, '2015-12-16 15:25:37', '2015-12-16 15:25:37', '<p class="p1">One of London\'s most popular Korean restaurants with celebrity chef<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Judy Joo at the helm,<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>JinJuu has been an instant hit. Situated in the very cool Carnaby Street JinJuu serves a range of different fun and casual dining concepts.</p>\n<p class="p1">A particular highlight of their menu is their “Anju” selection – which refers to food that you eat while you drink – so picture tacos, sliders and our and sharing platters all with a modern Korean/ Asian fusion.</p>\n<p class="p1">The main dining room has an open kitchen and Korean graffiti artwork provides a real treat for the eye, or for a more casual dining experience sit in the bar where on selected evenings their resident DJ transforms JinJuu into a really vibrant venue.</p>', 'JinJuu', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '97-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-16 15:25:37', '2015-12-16 15:25:37', '', 97, 'http://localhost:8888/mct-wordpress/97-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
